    "definitions": [
      {
        "index": 1,
        "gloss": "all of creation following their original natures, living and enjoying themselves freely",
        "register": "standard",
        "nuance": null,
        "scenarios": [],
        "sensory_tags": {
          "colors": [],
          "temperature": null,
          "sounds": [],
          "emotions": []
        },
        "collocations": [],
        "examples": {
          "standard": [
            {
              "text": "万物がそれぞれの天分を全うし、のびのびと生きる鳶飛魚躍の境地は、理想的な社会の姿と言える。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-3-flash-preview"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "窓の外に広がる豊かな自然を眺めていると、まさに鳶飛魚躍、命の輝きに満ち溢れているのがわかる。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-3-flash-preview"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "「無理に型に嵌めようとするな。鳶飛魚躍、子供たちが個性を自由に伸ばせるように見守るのが教育だ」",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-3-flash-preview"
              }
            }
          ],
          "literary": []
        }
      },
      {
        "index": 2,
        "gloss": "Heaven's will that all of creation shall follow their original natures and live freely",
        "register": "standard",
        "nuance": null,
        "scenarios": [],
        "sensory_tags": {
          "colors": [],
          "temperature": null,
          "sounds": [],
          "emotions": []
        },
        "collocations": [],
        "examples": {
          "standard": [
            {
              "text": "厳しい冬が終わり、芽吹く木々や跳ねる魚の姿に、鳶飛魚躍の自然の理を感じずにはいられない。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-3-flash-preview"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "画集の序文には、作者が追い求めた芸術の理想として「鳶飛魚躍」の四文字が力強く記されていた。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-3-flash-preview"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "「ああ、いい眺めだ。鳥は飛び魚は躍る、この鳶飛魚躍の風景こそが私の求めていた平穏だよ」",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-3-flash-preview"
              }
            }
          ],
          "literary": []
        }
      },
